'''Embassy Mall''' was a shopping center on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was located midway up the dome of the [[Nicandra Counterrevolutionary Signalmen's Memorial Building/Legends|Nicandra Counterrevolutionary Signalmen's Memorial Building]], and was open to the sky. During the [[Battle of Coruscant/Legends|Battle of Coruscant]], the owners refused to allow in any civilian refugees fleeing the fighting.

